UID:e03e18aec6798c5398748cf2bf003b41f59e39ed@macro-calendar.local
DTSTAMP:20260603T063057Z
DTSTART:20260122T133000Z
DTEND:20260122T140000Z
SUMMARY:🔥 US BEA: Gross Domestic Product\, 3rd Quarter 2025 (Updated E
 stimate)\, GDP by Industry\, and Corporate Profits (Revised)
DESCRIPTION:Source: US BEA\nImpact: high\nwww.bea.gov\n\nExplainer:\n• 
 What it is: Gross Domestic Product\n\n• Measures: Broad change in the 
 value of goods and services produced by the economy.\n\n• Usual market
  effect: Stronger-than-forecast GDP can be bullish for the local currenc
 y and equities\, although the reaction depends on inflation and rate exp
 ectations.\n\n• Why traders care: GDP is the broadest measure of econo
 mic growth and helps traders judge whether the economy is accelerating o
 r slowing.\n\n• Frequency: Quarterly\, with revisions.\n\n• Notes: G
 DP can be backward-looking\, so markets often react more strongly when t
 he result changes the outlook for central-bank policy or recession risk.
 \n\n• Acronyms: GDP = Gross Domestic Product.\n\nOfficial source: http
 s://www.bea.gov/news/schedule/ics/online-calendar-subscription.ics
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT24H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Tomorrow: 🔥 US BEA: Gross Domestic Product\, 3rd Quarter 2
 025 (Updated Estimate)\, GDP by Industry\, and Corporate Profits (Revise
 d)
END:VALARM
